{"service_name": "Cloud Design and Build Services", "service_id": "7105980621591072", "company_name": "Cognizant Technology Solutions UK Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Cognizant Technology Solutions UK Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Cloud Design and Build Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Cognizant\u2019s Cloud Services support planning, building and managing cloud environments with a portfolio of flexible choices (IaaS/ PaaS) across private, public and hybrid deployment models. They include our own hosted data center, partnered private cloud players and leading public cloud vendors like AWS, Azure, IBM.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Hybrid cloud setup\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Application re-hosting (Custom/ packaged applications)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     DR, storage, backup archival on cloud\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Desktop-aaS\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Dev, Test environment optimisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     DevOps on cloud\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Private/Hybrid PaaS\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     HPC optimisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Web apps on cloud\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Big data analytics\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Flexibility to scale up or down based on requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduce data centre footprint and standardisation across multiple sites\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Shift from CAPEX to OPEX models\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increase resource utilisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Seamless transition from development to testing\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Highly efficient systems driven by automated solutions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Faster speed to market with flexible development\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Drive efficiency in high computing batch processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Deliver system performance, real-time availability, pay per use model\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Build agile systems\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3117 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92235/7105980621591072-pricing-document-2015-10-05-1733.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92235/7105980621591072-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-05-2320.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92235/7105980621591072-service-definition-document-2015-10-05-1733.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         docu